pageProduct.name: U by Kotex Super Pads Wing Extra 14 Pack
pageProduct.description:
General Information

U By Kotex® Regular Extra pads offer maximum period protection and have got you covered no matter what. Cotton-like, soft, flexible, plus wings for some serious extra protection to reduce that annoying bunching and scrunching.

  • With fast absorbing blue core to provide greater protection by quickly drawing fluid into the pad
  • Secure wings to keep the pad firmly in place
  • All round channels designed to keep fluid in the centre helping to prevent leakage
  • Perfect for maximum protection during the day. 
  • Serious extra protection to reduce that annoying bunching and scrunching

Maximum Protection Pads

Boxed Contents: 14 Super Pads

Size: 14 Pack

Directions

Remove wrapper and peel strip in one quick move

STORAGE AND DISPOSAL

Do not flush
